<i>noun</i>: 쿠 클럭스 클랜 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>쿠 클럭스 클랜</dt><br>
<dd>a secret society of white Southerners in the United States; was formed in the 19th century to resist the emancipation of slaves; used terrorist tactics to suppress Black people</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Ku Klux Klan, Klan, KKK</dd><br>
